🏢 Real-world use case:
Multi-tenant SaaS Healthcare Platform:

Think of a company building:
Cloud-based Electronic Health Records (EHR) system

Customers:
Hospitals in India, EU, US
Each hospital = tenant

Data:
 •Patient records (PII + PHI)
 •Prescriptions
 •Medical history

🔐 Security + compliance requirements
 •Strong encryption (PHI data)
 •Per-tenant isolation
 •Data residency (EU data must stay in EU)
 •Key rotation
 •Right to be forgotten (key deletion)

